---
import Layout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Company Overview">
<!-- Company Profile -->
<section
  class="relative h-screen bg-center bg-cover snap-start"
  style="background-image: url('/company-profile.png');"
>
  <!-- Dark overlay -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-50"></div>

  <!-- Centered content -->
  <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-center h-full text-center text-white px-4">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Company Profile</h1>
    <p class="max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed">
      GC International FZCO is a leading distributor and specialist in high‑quality plug valves for Oil & Gas and chemical industries since 1919. Based in Solaro near Milan, Italy, our workshop and offices span over 12,000 m², supporting engineering excellence worldwide.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>


  <!-- Our History -->
<section class="snap-start h-screen bg-white flex items-center">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto w-full grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 px-6 py-12">
      <!-- Timeline Column -->
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gcBlue mb-10">Our History</h2>
        <div class="relative border-l-2 border-gcBlue pl-6 space-y-10">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gcBlue">1919</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Founded in Italy – the roots of the GC legacy begin.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gcBlue">1992</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">New factory established for offshore markets and petrochemical refineries.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gcBlue">2017</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">GC International opens its Dubai branch to serve MENA and Asia markets.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gcBlue">Today</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Dubai office supports global operations with regional logistics, sales, and service.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
  
      <!-- Image Column -->
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
        <img
          src="public/history.jpg"
          alt="GC Dubai Office"
          class="rounded-xl shadow-lg w-full max-w-md object-cover"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  

  <!-- Certifications -->
  <section class="bg-gray-100 py-20 snap-start">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gcBlue mb-6">Certifications & Quality</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Our Quality Management System is certified to ISO 9001, ISO 14001, and ISO 45001 by Lloyd’s Register. We also hold key industry certifications including API 6A, API 6D, PED, and ATEX. 
      </p>
      <ul class="text-gray-700 list-disc list-inside max-w-md mx-auto text-left">
        <li>API 6A</li>
        <li>API 6D</li>
        <li>PED</li>
        <li>ATEX</li>
        <li>ISO 9001:2015 • ISO 14001:2015 • ISO 45001:2018</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-gray-600 italic mt-4">
        “Quality for us is never the end of a process but the natural development of a philosophy…” 
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
